Interface DependencyRelation

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleDependencyRelation
public interface DependencyRelation

An interface for representing a dependency relationship between a head node and its dependent relation.

Method Summary
 DependencyTreeNode dependentNode()
          Returns the dependent node that is related to the head node.
 DependencyTreeNode headNode()
          Returns the head node on which the second node has dependent relation.
 String relation()
          Returns the relation the the current has with the next token in a DependencyPath.
